                     <hi rend="smallCaps">NOT GUILTY</hi>
                  </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Garrett was further charged with having been before convicted</hi>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18581025-name-347" type="witnessName">
